DOWN: Ezr, Dpy19l1, Igfbpl1, Dusp4, Pcdh18, Rnd2, Cntn2, Kif26a, [NA], Nuak1

### Cross-contrast notes
- **Olig1** appears as TOP UP in DIV2 vs DIV1 (LFC=+3.37)
  - Also appears as TOP DOWN in Netrin vs DIV2 (LFC=-1.00)
  - → Confirms "Netrin reverses DIV1→DIV2 progenitor activation" thesis
